No.55/4/CF-64 (i)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
IMMEDIATE
New Delhi, the 14th June 1964.
The undersigned is directed to state that, with effect
from the forenoon of Saturday, June 13, 1964, Shri Bali Ram Bhagat,
Minister (of State) of Planning, also assumed the office of
Minister of State in the Ministry of Finance in the Department of
Co-ordination.
(D.P. Chopra)
for Cabinet Secretary.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Principal Private Secretary
to the Prime Minister/the Private Secretary to the Prime
Minister, for information.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Private Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
P.T.0.

Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/Chairman,
Railway Board/Secretary, Election Commission, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Ministries of the Government
of India/Department of Parliamentary Affairs/Planning Commission/
Department of Atomic Energy/Prine Minister's Secretariat/
Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha Secretariat, for information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
1MANOCHAU
